<A>__{april stands at the stove over a pot of rolling, boiling water. she removes the rubber syringe from its paper packaging and drops it into the pot. she checks her watch.}
<L>__{interior wheeler hallway day.}
<A>__{april carries the pot of boiling, sudsy water down the hall.}
